# BOGBIN-0.1 first proof chain
# A -> B -> C, therefore claim_A_C is verifiable.

CREATE_NODE A
CREATE_NODE B
CREATE_NODE C

CREATE_EDGE A B support
CREATE_EDGE B C support

CREATE_CLAIM claim_A_C A C

ACTIVATE A 1000
PROPAGATE A support 2
INTERFERE claim_A_C
COMPUTE_TENSION claim_A_C
VERIFY claim_A_C
ACCEPT claim_A_C
EMIT_RECEIPT
HALT
